headline: Parker-Hannifin (PH) Gets Price Target Boost to $1,038 from Morgan Stanley
summary: Parker-Hannifin Corporation (NYSE:PH) is included among the Goldman Sachs Dividend Stocks: Top 14 Stock Picks. On February 24, Morgan Stanley raised its price recommendation on Parker-Hannifin Corporation (NYSE:PH) to $1,038 from $945. It reiterated an Equal Weight rating on the stock.
